WEBVTT

00:00:59.959 --> 00:01:03.243
And it touched me to the core.

00:01:05.529 --> 00:01:09.976
You know, you aspire for beauty,

00:01:11.310 --> 00:01:16.422
for sensuousness, for atmosphere,
the emotional response.

00:01:17.730 --> 00:01:20.262
That's the realm of the ineffable

00:01:20.286 --> 00:01:22.057
and the immeasurable.

00:01:22.081 --> 00:01:24.223
And that's what you live for:

00:01:24.971 --> 00:01:26.607
a chance to try.

00:01:27.858 --> 00:01:31.335
So in 2003, there was
an open call for designs